Package PaintTool

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColorPalette
    ColorPalette A class that contains two panels having backgrounds showing pen and fill colors Both panels are also implemented mouseListener to select multiple colors
    ColorPanel
    ColorPanel A class that extends JPanel and allows to select the color to set background
    DrawingHistory
    DrawingHistory A class that extends JPanel and implements ActionListener for showing all drawing operations supporting Undo option
    Menu
    Menu A class that extends the JMenuBar and adds necessary menu items
    Paint
    Paint A main application window contains all implemented panels
    PaintToolPanel
    PaintToolPanel A class contains instances of ToolButton classes and a reset button for clearing selected colors
    SquarePadDrawing
    SquarePadDrawing A Class that extends the JPanel and contains all the drawing logic with code
    Tool
    Tool A class used to create different Tool instances, with the given type parameter
    ToolButton
    ToolButton A class that extends JButton and implements ActionListener for each Tool button
    ToolDetails
    ToolDetails A class that extends the Tool class and provides a method for customizing the color
    ToolFactory
    ToolFactory A class that serves for creating the appropriate Tool class
  • Exception Summary

    VecFileException Class that extends the Exception to implement Exception in the application
